TEA OS v1.1.0 FILE System Commands:
create FILENAME
init FILENAME
write FILENAME
(rename | rn | mv | move) FILENAME NEWNAME
(copy|clone) FILE1 FILE2
exists FILENAME
find PATTERN
(show | cat | read) FILENAME
export FILENAME
(del | delete | rm) FILENAME
(ls | list | dir | files) PATTERN
